query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(it1 mi mc) NoMergeJoin(it1 mc mi ct) NoHashJoin(ct it1 mc mi cn) NoMergeJoin(cn ct it1 mc mi t) NoMergeJoin(cn ct it1 mc mi t mi_idx) NoMergeJoin(cn ct it1 mc mi mi_idx t it2) */ select min(cn.name) AS movie_company,
min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS drama_horror_movie
from info_type AS it1
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mi.info_type_id = it1.id AND it1.info = 'genres' AND mi.info IN ('Western',
'Thriller')
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies'
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1997 AND 2013
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info > '10'
inner join info_type AS it2
on mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id AND it2.info = 'rating';
